videos.description: Texas' Matt Coleman lobs it high to Jaxson Hayes, who throws down a monster alley-oop slam over Texas Tech defenders.
videos.headline: Hayes throws down vicious alley-oop slam

videos.description: Texas Tech's Norense Odiase is left alone under the basket as he throws down a monster two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Odiase gets up for monster slam

videos.description: Texas' Kerwin Roach throws it up to Jaxson Hayes who slams it down, his 2nd alley-oop jam of the game.
videos.headline: Hayes slams home alley-oop jam
